.IX Title "More 3"
.TH More 3 "perl v5.6.1" "1998-11-03" "User Contributed Perl Documentation"
.UC
.SH "NAME"
Tk::More \- a 'more' or 'less' like text widget
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 1
\&    use Tk::More;
.Ve
.Vb 2
\&    $more = $parent->More(...text widget options ...);
\&    $more->Load(FILENAME);
.Ve
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
\&\fBTk::More\fR is a readonly text widget with additional key bindings as
found in UNI* command line tool \f(CW\*(C`more\*(C'\fR.  As in \f(CW\*(C`more\*(C'\fR an additional
status/command line is added at the bottom.
.SH "ADDITIONAL BINDINGS"
.IX Header "ADDITIONAL BINDINGS"
.Ip "Key-G" 4
.IX Item "Key-G"
goto end of file
.Ip "Key-f" 4
.IX Item "Key-f"
like next key
.Ip "Key-b" 4
.IX Item "Key-b"
like prior key
.Ip "Key-k" 4
.IX Item "Key-k"
like up key
.Ip "Key-j" 4
.IX Item "Key-j"
like down key
.Ip "Key-/" 4
.IX Item "Key-/"
search forward
.Ip "Key-n" 4
.IX Item "Key-n"
find next match
.Ip "Key-N" 4
.IX Item "Key-N"
find previous match
.SH "BUGS"
.IX Header "BUGS"
Besides that most of more bindings are not implemented. This bugs
me most (high to low priority):
.PP
* Reverse search missing
.PP
* better status line implementation
.PP
* Cursor movement: up/down move displayed area regardless where
  insert cursor is
.PP
* add History, Load, Search (also as popup menu)
.PP
* Key-u and Key-d should move 1/2 screen and not 90% of a screen
.PP
* bad history impl.
